name: InspireMe
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
This skill provides you a new compliment everyday. And why do we need compliments? We don't, but it is an amazing boost in your life that you wouldn't want to miss. Studies show that compliments makes you feel better and increases your performance in real life (See article: https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0048174)
Just open Inspire Me skill by calling "Alexa, open Inspire Me" and you will get your daily reward in the form of a sweet compliment.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
